  "detailed_description": "Dino Survivors is a game inspired by great hits of the roguelite genre, with a 'pixel art' artistic style and simple, automatic gameplay so you can start going out hunting prehistoric creatures without the need to learn complex systems!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use primitive tools to survive and explore a prehistoric world!</h2>Explore different scenarios and combinations of primitive tools, with several playable characters to try to reach the big boss in each area.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/4d35202cafca422e9c0f78f189146918.poster.avif?t=1700832572\" width=174 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/4d35202cafca422e9c0f78f189146918.webm?t=1700832572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/4d35202cafca422e9c0f78f189146918.mp4?t=1700832572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/34866f1676f1fe6670ac624c935b6845.poster.avif?t=1700832572\" width=174 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/34866f1676f1fe6670ac624c935b6845.webm?t=1700832572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/34866f1676f1fe6670ac624c935b6845.mp4?t=1700832572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/40de6f11f6912ad05b59d5f396978ab3.poster.avif?t=1700832572\" width=174 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/40de6f11f6912ad05b59d5f396978ab3.webm?t=1700832572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/40de6f11f6912ad05b59d5f396978ab3.mp4?t=1700832572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play and Discover</h2>Each Enemy has unique characteristics and different attack patterns that make the game very challenging. Discover dozens of different species of fantastic animals that once existed, as well as learning a little more about their characteristics and behaviors.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/606eeb8ee5eb35d6bb9b4a7ae22959ae.poster.avif?t=1700832572\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/606eeb8ee5eb35d6bb9b4a7ae22959ae.webm?t=1700832572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/606eeb8ee5eb35d6bb9b4a7ae22959ae.mp4?t=1700832572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Secrets and Collectibles</h2>Find all the Tools and secrets hidden in the game with the unlockable system, collections and dozens of achievements for those who like to explore.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/9b67dc279e56dc806c3d778f20467e6d.avif?t=1700832572\" width=600 height=88 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Dino Survivors is a game inspired by great hits of the roguelite genre, with a 'pixel art' artistic style and simple, automatic gameplay so you can start going out hunting prehistoric creatures without the need to learn complex systems!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use primitive tools to survive and explore a prehistoric world!</h2>Explore different scenarios and combinations of primitive tools, with several playable characters to try to reach the big boss in each area.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/4d35202cafca422e9c0f78f189146918.poster.avif?t=1700832572\" width=174 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/4d35202cafca422e9c0f78f189146918.webm?t=1700832572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/4d35202cafca422e9c0f78f189146918.mp4?t=1700832572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/34866f1676f1fe6670ac624c935b6845.poster.avif?t=1700832572\" width=174 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/34866f1676f1fe6670ac624c935b6845.webm?t=1700832572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/34866f1676f1fe6670ac624c935b6845.mp4?t=1700832572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/40de6f11f6912ad05b59d5f396978ab3.poster.avif?t=1700832572\" width=174 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/40de6f11f6912ad05b59d5f396978ab3.webm?t=1700832572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/40de6f11f6912ad05b59d5f396978ab3.mp4?t=1700832572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play and Discover</h2>Each Enemy has unique characteristics and different attack patterns that make the game very challenging. Discover dozens of different species of fantastic animals that once existed, as well as learning a little more about their characteristics and behaviors.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/606eeb8ee5eb35d6bb9b4a7ae22959ae.poster.avif?t=1700832572\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/606eeb8ee5eb35d6bb9b4a7ae22959ae.webm?t=1700832572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/606eeb8ee5eb35d6bb9b4a7ae22959ae.mp4?t=1700832572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Secrets and Collectibles</h2>Find all the Tools and secrets hidden in the game with the unlockable system, collections and dozens of achievements for those who like to explore.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639840/extras/9b67dc279e56dc806c3d778f20467e6d.avif?t=1700832572\" width=600 height=88 /></span>",
